title: Vista Training (Working)
description:
My apologies for the first one I didn&#039;t test it first this one will autoplay and is an awesome directory tree file.

From M$ themselves. Training for retail consumer manufacturers. Geared towards Tech Support for the consumer. This is great info on the newest in the line of OS&#039;s from M$. Everything form HOW-TO&#039;S to HOW-NOT-TO&#039;s. Designed to push out to manufacturer Tech Support, for the beginner to the higher level user. What can I say everthing M$ won&#039;t support but let the retailers do. I can&#039;t say enough about this material for what is out there now. Haven&#039;t seen any instruction manuals better than this. Everything the new Vista can and cant do. Step by step guides on how to break it and to fix it. Good stuff.
